  "description": "<i>Wizard of Words</i> contains a number of fantasy themed word games.<br><br>There are 5 games in total with 8 levels of difficulty with each challenge:<ul>\n<li>Castle Capers: a <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Hangman\">Hangman</a> variant, where the player attempts to guess a word before a gate slams shut.</li><br>\n<li>Dragon's Spell: 1 - 2 player game where the players try to make as many smaller words as possible from the letters of a larger word.</li><br>\n<li>Herald's Hark: try to guess a 3 - 5 letter word.  For each word, the player is told how many letters are correct.</li><br>\n<li>Jester's Jumble: unscramble the displayed word.  There are 8 levels of difficulty.</li><br>\n<li>Word Spinning: players take turns filling words into a crossword, and are awarded one points for each correct letter.</li></ul>",
